text.tspan: PolyOS 6 comes with a coding language called PolyScript.
Lets learn how to make your own apps for PolyOS!
There are 2 main ways to make an app for PolyOS 6.
The first way is to remix PolyOS 6, clone the window template,
and then design your own sprites, UI, etc. This way favors looks
and functionality over easiness to install. People will need to also
remix to import and use your app.
Another way to code is using PolyScript, which can be coded on
right from PolyOS. Apps made with PolyScript are far less functional
but are as easy as loading a save code. They can also be installed in
PolyOS without remixing. More info can be found in the description.
